long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get ready to collect candies falling from the air with a sweet duck! Avoid obstacles and make the highest score.

How To Play
Played with Mouse.

Baby Duck Casual Game Features
✓ 2D Character
✓ Infinity Level
✓ Easy control
✓ Fun Sounds

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Baby Duck Casual Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
